OL,7,FToday Habibur Masum, 25, appeared at
OL,8,FBradford Magistrates Court charged
OL,9,Fwith her murder.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News in Bangladesh,
OL,12,FKulsuma's mother said: "I don't want
OL,13,Fanything else, I just want a true
OL,14,Fjudgement for my child ... no other
OL,15,Fmum should suffer like me, no child
OL,16,Fshould be taken away from their mum."
OL,18,FKulsuma's baby is safe and was not
OL,19,Fharmed in the incident, police said.
