OL,7,FThe grandmother, who lives in
OL,8,FBangladesh, said: "On the day she died
OL,9,FI was praying, I didn't talk to her.
OL,11,F"I spoke to her the day before at
OL,12,FSehri time (when Muslims observing
OL,13,FRamadan will eat before fasting, just
OL,14,Fbefore dawn).
OL,16,F"We exchanged pleasantries. My
OL,17,Fgrandchild was in her arms my
OL,18,Fgrandchild wanted to come to me.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/6
