OL,7,F"After which my grandchild was crying
OL,8,Floads that they want to come to me. So
OL,9,Fshe said mum let me put the phone down
OL,10,Fand also it's time to eat.
OL,12,F"That was the last time I spoke to
OL,13,Fher."
OL,15,FShe says Ms Akter was her youngest
OL,16,Fdaughter who "always looked after her."
OL,18,F"I loved my daughter. I want a
OL,19,Fjudgement," she said through tears.
