OL,7,FMasum, of Leamington Avenue, Burnley,
OL,8,Fis also charged with possession of a
OL,9,Fbladed article.
OL,11,FWearing a grey sweatshirt and flanked
OL,12,Fby two dock officers he spoke only to
OL,13,Fconfirm his name and date of birth.
OL,15,FHe was sent to Bradford Crown Court
OL,16,Ffor a hearing and was remanded in
OL,17,Fcustody by District Judge Alex Boyd.
OL,19,FMr Masum was arrested in Aylesbury,
OL,20,FBuckinghamshire, in the early hours of
OL,21,FTuesday.
